1171
01:19:11,456 --> 01:19:13,855
Gerçek aşkıyla birlikte o.

1172
01:19:20,410 --> 01:19:21,793
Ne oluyor?

1173
01:19:24,295 --> 01:19:26,114
Anna.

1174
01:19:51,393 --> 01:19:53,133
Yardım edin.

1175
01:19:57,833 --> 01:20:00,473
